arts.ttl: Lionel Messi has goal and assist for Inter Miami in 3-1 MLS win over Seattle Sounders
arts.sum: The Sounders beat Inter Miami 3-0 in the Leagues Cup on Aug. 31, but Messi assisted a wide open Jordi Alba with an outside-of-the-foot pass in the 12th minute to give the Herons early command. Lionel Messi had a goal and an assist as Inter Miami beat Seattle 3-1 on Tuesday night just over two weeks after losing to the Sounders in the Leagues Cup final.

arts.ttl: Inter Miami vs. Seattle Sounders: Preview, Predictions and Lineups
arts.sum: Seattle Sounders look to clinch an MLS Cup Playoff berth against the struggling Herons.

arts.ttl: Inter Miami Predicted Lineup vs. Seattle Sounders: Leagues Cup Rematch Beckons
arts.sum: The Herons have won just one of their last four matches in all competitions.
